1619
01:19:14,700 --> 01:19:17,095
and now you can see
why this sum works.

1620
01:19:17,095 --> 01:19:21,110
R is the number of men to
get the right hat back.

1621
01:19:21,110 --> 01:19:24,210
And it basically there's a
one counted in here every time

1622
01:19:24,210 --> 01:19:28,740
a guy gets his hat back,
and 0 if he doesn't.

1623
01:19:28,740 --> 01:19:33,276
So this sum is counting how many
men got their right hat back.

1624
01:19:33,276 --> 01:19:36,280


1625
01:19:36,280 --> 01:19:38,980
Non-obvious the first
time, gets really simple

1626
01:19:38,980 --> 01:19:41,420
the fourth or fifth time.

1627
01:19:41,420 --> 01:19:43,896
We'll try to do a
couple of them today.

1628
01:19:43,896 --> 01:19:48,290


1629
01:19:48,290 --> 01:19:52,505
All right, now the expected
